          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="wm-prize" data-wm-reveal style="background-image:url('https://mallorcadistillery.com/cdn/shop/files/Low_Res_-_006_1024x1024.jpg?width=1200')">
          <div class="wm-prize-body">
            <span class="wm-prize-tag">Every month</span>
            <h3>A complete <span class="wm-ital">Palma set</span></h3>
            <p>Each month we pick our favourite entries to win a full Palma collection — the organic range delivered to your door.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

